title: 3 Questions to a Happier Life
itunes:title: 3 Questions to a Happier Life
description:
Episode 577 - There is so much resistance in your life that you don't even realize is there. The problem is that you also don't realize how much it slows you down on a daily basis. If you were able to remove that resistance, you would finally be able to run at full speed. We are talking about the most efficient version of yourself. In this episode, I will teach you how to identify the places of most resistance in your life and how to get rid of them.
